Titolo: Crystal Monsters

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Crystal Monsters, originally released in Japan in 2008 as Monster Chronicle for mobile phone, is a role-playing video game developed by Gameloft for Nintendo DSiWare. The game was released in PAL regions on July 30, 2010 and in North America on July 26, 2010.
Crystal Monsters is played in a third-person view overhead perspective and takes place in a fictional world called Earth in which the player navigates the main character.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
